=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h1 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam Pro&quot;;font-style:normal;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-size:1em;line-height:1.7;\">TI\u1ec6N \u00cdCH VINHOMES H\u1ea2I V\u00c2N BAY<\/h1><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-right\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Trong quy ho\u1ea1ch 512ha b\u00ean v\u1ecbnh L\u00e0ng V\u00e2n,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/\"><strong data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"355\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p k\u00edn v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o theo m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u201call-in-one\u201d \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Vinhomes, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, n\u01a1i m\u1ed7i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m 5 sao.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-2\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>Ti\u1ec7n \u00edch t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng khai th\u00e1c \u1ed3 \u1ea1t, m\u00e0 d\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn di\u1ec7n t\u00edch cho kh\u00f4ng gian xanh, c\u1ea3nh quan m\u1eb7t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u1eeba t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n nghi, v\u1eeba c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng sinh th\u00e1i b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u201cchu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng Vinhomes\u201d m\u00e0 kh\u00f3 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0o s\u00e1nh k\u1ecbp.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-2 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"Vincom Center Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm, \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cao c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng tinh hoa.\" title=\"vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5444\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/vincom-center-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vincom Center Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng, h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm, \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cao c\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng tinh hoa.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-4\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>N\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch l\u00e0\u00a0<strong data-start=\"1252\" data-end=\"1277\">b\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<\/strong>\u00a0quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn, n\u01a1i c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn h\u1ea3i tr\u00ecnh xa hoa ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u gi\u1eefa l\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc xanh bi\u1ebfc. K\u1ec1 b\u00ean l\u00e0\u00a0<strong data-start=\"1451\" data-end=\"1472\">s\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n<\/strong>\u00a0chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, v\u1eeba mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn h\u01b0\u1edbng bi\u1ec3n ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-3 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"B\u1ebfn du thuy\u1ec1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eb9n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u, n\u01a1i c\u01b0 d\u00e2n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ngay t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.\" title=\"ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/ben-du-thuyen-quoc-te-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\