ee1ng<\/strong>, trung t\u00e2m\u00a0<strong data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1728\">spa &amp; wellness<\/strong>\u00a0ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khu\u00a0<strong data-start=\"1784\" data-end=\"1801\">gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed bi\u1ec3n<\/strong>\u00a0v\u1edbi \u0111a d\u1ea1ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 l\u01b0\u1edbt s\u00f3ng, ch\u00e8o sup, l\u1eb7n ng\u1eafm san h\u00f4, kayak\u2026 s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-4 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" alt=\"S\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ec3 thao sang tr\u1ecdng, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung.\" title=\"san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5442\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201080%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271080%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/san-golf-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay-da-nang.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-7\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">S\u00e2n golf ven bi\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ec3 thao sang tr\u1ecdng, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh quan n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n h\u00f9ng v\u0129 hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-8\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nhu c\u1ea7u mua s\u1eafm \u2013 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi\u00a0Vincom Center,\u00a0ph\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u2013 shophouse\u00a0ven bi\u1ec3n, c\u00f9ng khu\u00a0\u1ea9m th\u1ef1c qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i mua s\u1eafm, th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u2013 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, thu h\u00fat du kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i cho d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-5 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1081\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ven bi\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n xanh m\u00e1t, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.\" title=\"cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5441\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271081%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%201920%201081%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%271920%27%20height%3D%271081%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg-1200x676.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/cong-vien-ven-bien-vinhomes-hai-van-bay.jpg.jpg 1920w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-9\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean ven bi\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n xanh m\u00e1t, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-10\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-23\">\n<p>V\u1ec1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c \u2013 y t\u1ebf, Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay t\u00edch h\u1ee3p\u00a0<strong data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2379\">tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf Vinschool<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0<strong data-start=\"2383\" data-end=\"2403\">b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Vinmec<\/strong>, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ed1ng d\u00e0i l\u00e2u cho c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-24\">\n<p data-start=\"2589\" data-end=\"2980\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u2013 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chu\u1ea9n Vinhomes k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 AI, IoT trong gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, gi\u00fap c\u01b0 d\u00e2n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng an to\u00e0n, th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n. An ninh \u0111a l\u1edbp 24\/7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho m\u1ed7i gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2982\" data-end=\"3231\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch t\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh theo chu\u1ea9n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao. T\u1eeb l\u1ec5 t\u00e2n, d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ea3nh quan \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eb7t tour, \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e9, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n h\u00f3a, mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ed1ng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-image-element \" style=\"text-align:center;--awb-caption-title-font-family:var(--h2_typography-font-family);--awb-caption-title-font-weight:var(--h2_typography-font-weight);--awb-caption-title-font-style:var(--h2_typography-font-style);--awb-caption-title-size:var(--h2_typography-font-size);--awb-caption-title-transform:var(--h2_typography-text-transform);--awb-caption-title-line-height:var(--h2_typography-line-height);--awb-caption-title-letter-spacing:var(--h2_typography-letter-spacing);\"><span class=\" fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-6 hover-type-none\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1238\" alt=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh, an to\u00e0n 24\/7.\" title=\"H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh, an to\u00e0n 24\/7.\" src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247.jpg\" data-orig-src=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247.jpg\" class=\"lazyload img-responsive wp-image-5048\" srcset=\"data:image\/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%272200%27%20height%3D%271238%27%20viewBox%3D%270%200%202200%201238%27%3E%3Crect%20width%3D%272200%27%20height%3D%271238%27%20fill-opacity%3D%220%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-200x113.jpg 200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-400x225.jpg 400w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-800x450.jpg 800w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/vinhomehaivanbay.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/He-thong-kiem-soat-an-ninh-an-toan-247.jpg 2200w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/span><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-11\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:center;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh, an to\u00e0n 24\/7.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-12\" style=\"--awb-content-alignment:justify;\"><p data-start=\"3257\" data-end=\"3557\">H\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch 5 sao t\u1ea1i Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u sinh ho\u1ea1t, ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. M\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh thanh kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng sinh l\u1eddi d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3559\" data-end=\"3990\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa ti\u1ec7n \u00edch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan sinh th\u00e1i n\u00fai \u2013 bi\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3. C\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00ecnh minh tr\u00ean b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n ri\u00eang, v\u1eeba th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n trong c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean xanh, ch\u01a1i golf bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u hay mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n Trung.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3992\" data-end=\"4251\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i,\u00a0<strong data-start=\"4004\" data-end=\"4028\">Vinhomes H\u1ea3i V\u00e2n Bay<\/strong>\u00a0kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201cthi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch\u201d kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p s\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 \u00e1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng tinh hoa trong n\u0103m 2025.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-3 fusion-flex-container hundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-background-blend-mode:color;--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-background-color:#f5f1e6;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-align-content-flex-start fusion-flex-justify-content-center fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"width:104% !important;max-width:104% !important;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-2 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-title-center fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-two\" style=\"--awb-text-color:#000000;--awb-margin-top:20px;--awb-font-size:24px;\"><div class=\"title-sep-container title-sep-container-left\"><div class=\"title-sep sep-single sep-solid\" style=\"border-color:#000000;\"><\/div><\/div><span class=\"awb-title-spacer\"><\/span><h2 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-center\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Be Vietnam 